Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: The unidentified Padawan was a Nautolan Padawan who served under Jedi Master Denfa during the Third Galactic War. Both the apprentice and their master were slain on Onderon during the conflict there.
The Padawan was proficient in using the Force and was able to use Force Push and Force Shockwave. He could also use the Force to heal himself if injured in battle.
